{"tid":1685641,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"NYT Photographer Returns to the Battle Site of Hong Kong","createTime":"2019-10-31T16:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T16:02:05.000Z","uid":36073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9171d42972e688ffe1e36b33ec9ee5e718e0385","tid":1685641,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>Hong Kong Protests: Compare These Before-and-After Photos</strong><br />\n<br />\nA photographer returned to the sites of protests he documented in recent months. His diptychs show how life returns to normal, even if briefly, as the antigovernment movement continues.<br />\n<br />\nSham Shui Po Protest, 11th August<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2019/10/21/world/00hk-diptychs-1left/merlin_159146613_a5cbebf8-3738-43cc-8991-c2472a1e989e-jumbo.jpg?quality=90&amp;auto=webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2019%2F10%2F21%2Fworld%2F00hk-diptychs-1left%2Fmerlin_159146613_a5cbebf8-3738-43cc-8991-c2472a1e989e-jumbo.jpg%3Fquality%3D90%26auto%3Dwebp&h=9447187c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2019/10/21/world/00hk-diptychs-1right/merlin_162937689_42676d51-8240-4ed3-b940-416f6db0ccf0-jumbo.jpg?quality=90&amp;auto=webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2019%2F10%2F21%2Fworld%2F00hk-diptychs-1right%2Fmerlin_162937689_42676d51-8240-4ed3-b940-416f6db0ccf0-jumbo.jpg%3Fquality%3D90%26auto%3Dwebp&h=9b04f02e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA Million March, 9th June<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2019/10/21/world/00hk-diptychs-2left/merlin_156207387_b7e9b7e8-6ee5-468c-b36d-3131464508e0-jumbo.jpg?quality=90&amp;auto=webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2019%2F10%2F21%2Fworld%2F00hk-diptychs-2left%2Fmerlin_156207387_b7e9b7e8-6ee5-468c-b